Transaction Amount (authorized user)
Inability to add a transaction to the "Expenses" tab with a value <1 in the "Transaction Amount" field
Inability to add a transaction to the "Expenses" tab with a non-numeric value in the "Transaction Amount" field

Input button (authorized user)
Inability to click the "Input" button in the "Expenses" tab
When valid data is entered and the "Input" button is clicked in the "Expenses" tab, the transaction will appear in the transactions list
When valid data is entered and the "Input" button is clicked in the "Expenses" tab, the balance will decrease by the transaction amount
When valid data is entered and the "Input" button is clicked in the "Expenses" tab, the monthly summary value will increase by the transaction amount
When invalid data is entered and the "Input" button is clicked in the "Expenses" tab, the transaction will not appear in the transactions list
When invalid data is entered and the "Input" button is clicked in the "Expenses" tab, the balance will not decrease by the transaction amount
When invalid data is entered and the "Input" button is clicked in the "Expenses" tab, the monthly summary value will not increase by the transaction amount
Inability to click the "Input" button in the "Income" tab
When valid data is entered and the "Input" button is clicked in the "Income" tab, the transaction will appear in the transactions list
When valid data is entered and the "Input" button is clicked in the "Income" tab, the balance will increase by the transaction amount
When valid data is entered and the "Input" button is clicked in the "Income" tab, the monthly summary value will increase by the transaction amount
When invalid data is entered and the "Input" button is clicked in the "Income" tab, the transaction will not appear in the transactions list
When invalid data is entered and the "Input" button is clicked in the "Income" tab, the balance will not increase by the transaction amount
When invalid data is entered and the "Input" button is clicked in the "Income" tab, the monthly summary value will not increase by the transaction amount

In the "Expenses" tab, the balance increases when an existing transaction is deleted
In the "Income" tab, the balance decreases when an existing transaction is deleted
The displayed balance in the monthly summary will decrease when a transaction is deleted from the selected month

Deleting an income transaction is reflected in the summary
Ability to display income amounts, provided there is income for each month from 01 January 2024 to the current month of the current year
Ability to display income amounts, provided there is income for each month from 01 January 2023 to 31 December 2023

Perform a transition to the "Report" page
